<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Rayed" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Rayed</orth> (O. Edd. <emph>raied</emph> or <emph>raide</emph>) defiled, dirtied: <cit><quote>r. with the yellows,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 54</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>was ever man so beaten? was ever man so r.? was ever man so weary?</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 3</bibl></cit>.
